name: Sine Qua Non 2.15 (Experiplay+)//scene01
description: Kids are taught about abstract, conceptual and practical tools that made the plays more meaningful and impactful.   As a child grew in his faculties, the play should evolve, not disappear. Pioneers 'plays' a whole lot; experimenting all the time with new ideas and tools. And these exploration leads to new discoveries, which in time becomes the future's standard.
